  "description": "The Lorenz attractor as instrument, not texture. chaosIndex 0.05 — barely above the fixed point, the system choosing orbit over collapse. Leash 0.95: maximum phase-lock, the attractor held tight to pitch center. theta 1.571 (Z-axis from OURO-III) for warmth; phi 0.785 for full stereo separation. What remains is near-periodic, warm, and stable — a sound that no pure oscillator can replicate because the subtle attractor irregularities are still present, still breathing, just leashed. The chaos is real. It is simply held.",
